<td class="content" valign="top" height="90" width="350">The purpose of this tutorial is to provide a fundamental understanding of the purpose and application of variables in Flash ActionScript (both 1.0 and 2.0). This tutorial is aimed at beginners with no programming experience but is also suitable for programmers accustomed to other languages who wish to learn about Flash's syntax.

